{"tid":1076222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[毓民炒車系列] 國台辦:挺韓國瑜訪港 民進黨不願面對一國兩制的成功!","createTime":"2019-03-24T16:37:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-24T16:37:08.000Z","uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d6a5348da95cae973df625d7d55abca2c81b5483","tid":1076222,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T16:37:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190324/640_b1e73746a1e1ae19b0ede0ccd0f63b50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190324%2F640_b1e73746a1e1ae19b0ede0ccd0f63b50.jpg&h=c4f5f9ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高雄市長韓國瑜上任後首次訪問香港和澳門，獲安排與香港中聯辦主任王志民和澳門中聯辦主任傅自應會面，但遭到蔡政府全面圍剿，對此，中國國台辦旗下的官網「中國台灣網」力挺韓國瑜，批民進黨不願面對一國兩制實踐的成功。<br />\n<br />\n中國國台辦旗下的官網「中國台灣網」，刊出《民進黨為何如此挑剔韓國瑜港澳行？不願面對一國兩制實踐的成功？》文章，指出韓國瑜的港澳之行成果顯著，採購合約超過34億元，毫無疑問是相當成功的，但台灣一些綠營人士，還是本能地加以政治解讀，多有挑剔批評「抹黑抹紅」。<br />\n<br />\n文章指出，港澳回歸後的發展進步是有目共睹的，台灣不少人對港澳的一國兩制是有陳見、偏見、甚至是惡意的。眼見為實，看了就知道。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190324/1539027/?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=twad_article_share&amp;utm_content=share_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190324%2F1539027%2F%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dtwad_article_share%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6VuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=8e256a9a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190324%2F1539027%2F%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dtwad_article_share%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&h=193971a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190324/1539027/?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=twad_article_share&amp;utm_content=share_link</a>"}]}